---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Quick Start" description="Get Engrams running in your project in under five minutes.">
  <h1>Quick Start</h1>
  <p class="lead">
    From zero to a fully-loaded project memory in five minutes.
    Make sure you have completed the <a href="/docs/installation">installation</a> first.
  </p>

  <div class="steps">

    <!-- Step 1 -->
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Bootstrap from existing docs (optional)</h3>
        <p>
          If you already have a <code>README.md</code>, architecture doc, or similar, ask your AI
          to read and store the key information in Engrams:
        </p>
        <pre><code>{`You: Read my README.md and docs/ARCHITECTURE.md and store
     the key decisions, patterns, and project context in Engrams.

AI:  [ENGRAMS_ACTIVE] Engrams initialized.
     Architectural patterns stored.
     Coding standard decisions recorded.

     What would you like to work on?`}</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 2 -->
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Log your first decisions</h3>
        <p>Start a conversation and tell your AI about important choices:</p>
        <pre><code>{`You: The team has decided to use PostgreSQL as our primary database
     because we need ACID guarantees and complex query support.

AI:  Decision logged to Engrams:
     Decision #1: Use PostgreSQL for primary database
     Rationale: ACID guarantees, complex queries, mature ecosystem
     Tags: database, architecture`}</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 3 -->
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Watch context surface automatically</h3>
        <p>Now ask your AI to implement something:</p>
        <pre><code>{`You: Add a new /users endpoint to the API

AI:  I'll help with that. Retrieving project context...

     Found Decision #1: PostgreSQL is the primary database
     Found Decision #7: JWT auth required on all routes
     Found Pattern #2: Structured error handling

     Implementing with SQLAlchemy, JWT middleware,
     and proper error responses...`}</code></pre>
        <p>
          The AI found those decisions <em>automatically</em> — you didn't have to mention them.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <h2>What to try next</h2>
  <div class="next-cards">
    <a href="/docs/features/team-sync" class="next-card">
      <span class="nc-icon">🔄</span>
      <strong>Team Sync</strong>
      <span>Share decisions via <code>.engrams/</code> and Git</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/docs/features/governance" class="next-card">
      <span class="nc-icon">🛡️</span>
      <strong>Team Governance</strong>
      <span>Enforce team-level architectural mandates</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/docs/features/bindings" class="next-card">
      <span class="nc-icon">🔗</span>
      <strong>Codebase Bindings</strong>
      <span>Bind decisions to file paths so context follows the code</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/docs/features/dashboard" class="next-card">
      <span class="nc-icon">📊</span>
      <strong>Knowledge Dashboard</strong>
      <span>Visually explore your project's knowledge graph</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>

<style>
  .lead { font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }

  .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
  .step {
    display: flex; gap: 1.25rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .step-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 2rem; height: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--sky-aqua), var(--maya-blue));
    color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: .875rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin-top: .1rem;
  }
  .step-body { flex: 1; }
  .step-body h3 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.05rem; }

  .next-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(210px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .next-card {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .35rem;
    background: var(--color-bg); border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.25rem;
    text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);
    transition: border-color .15s, box-shadow .15s, transform .15s;
  }
  .next-card:hover { border-color: var(--sky-aqua); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); transform: translateY(-2px); text-decoration: none; }
  .nc-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; }
  .next-card strong { font-size: .9375rem; }
  .next-card span { font-size: .8125rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }
</style>
